description: This file is a C header file (.h) that declares the interface for the Beep Master Servlet Object (MSO) in the BSP Execution Environment Plane Implementation. It contains macro guards, license and copyright information, module description, environment and author metadata, and prototype declarations for factory and lifecycle functions related to the Beep Master Servlet.

methods.name: BeepCreateMasterServlet
methods.description: Creates and returns a handle to the Beep Master Servlet object, taking container, owner, and reserved context handles as parameters.

methods.name: BeepMsoCreate
methods.description: Creates and returns a handle to a Beep Master Servlet object, with container, owner, and reserved context handles.

methods.name: BeepMsoRemove
methods.description: Removes or deallocates the Beep Master Servlet object associated with the given handle.

methods.name: BeepMsoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls required objects into the Beep MSO, likely for setup or initialization.

methods.name: BeepMsoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Beep MSO object, setting up internal states or configurations.
